Stephen T. McLin

Age : 70Public asset : 7,145,365 USDLinked companies :  Charles Schwab Corp 





Summary 



Mr. Stephen T. McLin is Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at STM Holdings LLC.He is on the Board of Directors at The Charles Schwab Corp. and Charles Schwab Bank. Mr. McLin was previously employed as President & Chief Executive Officer by America First Financial Corp. and Executive Vice President by Bank of America Corp.



