Individual




Stephen T. McLin



Mr. Stephen T. McLin is Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at STM Holdings LLC and Independent Director at The Charles Schwab Corp. He is on the Board of Directors at The Charles Schwab Corp. and Charles Schwab Bank.
Mr. McLin was previously employed as President & Chief Executive Officer by America First Financial Corp. and Executive Vice President by Bank of America Corp.



